<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">
<title>InvestingPro.in — Free Data Intelligence Map</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#06080F;--c1:#0D1117;--c2:#111827;--c3:#1A2235;--c4:#212D42;
  --br:#1E2A3E;--br2:#263348;
  --t1:#F0F4FF;--t2:#8B9EC4;--t3:#4A5A7A;
  --vi:#6C63FF;--vix:rgba(108,99,255,.12);
  --gr:#00D084;--grx:rgba(0,208,132,.1);
  --am:#FF9F43;--amx:rgba(255,159,67,.1);
  --cy:#22D3EE;--cyx:rgba(34,211,238,.1);
  --re:#FF5B5B;--rex:rgba(255,91,91,.1);
  --pk:#F72585;--pkx:rgba(247,37,133,.1);
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html,body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--t1);font-family:'IBM Plex Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:13px;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;line-height:1.6}
.wrap{max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;padding:36px 24px}

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero{text-align:center;padding:52px 0 44px;position:relative}
.hero::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 900px 400px at 50% 0%,rgba(108,99,255,.07),transparent);pointer-events:none}
.eyebrow{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--vi);margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px}
.eyebrow::before,.eyebrow::after{content:'';width:32px;height:1px;background:var(--vi)}
h1{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.04em;color:var(--t1);margin-bottom:12px}
h1 span{color:var(--gr)}
.hero-sub{font-size:14.5px;color:var(--t2);max-width:580px;margin:0 auto 20px;line-height:1.7}
.hero-chips{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.hc{padding:4px 13px;border:1px solid var(--br2);border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;color:var(--t3);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace}
.hc.gr{border-color:rgba(0,208,132,.25);color:var(--gr)}.hc.vi{border-color:rgba(108,99,255,.25);color:var(--vi)}.hc.am{border-color:rgba(255,159,67,.25);color:var(--am)}.hc.cy{border-color:rgba(34,211,238,.25);color:var(--cy)}

/* ── SECTION HEADERS ── */
.section{margin-bottom:44px}
.section-hd{margin-bottom:18px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--br)}
.section-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:8.5px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--t3);margin-bottom:6px}
.section-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:19px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t1);letter-spacing:-.03em}
.section-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--t2);margin-top:4px;max-width:640px}

/* ── SOURCE CARDS ── */
.source-grid{display:grid;gap:14px}
.grid-2{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
.grid-3{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr}
.grid-4{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}

.source-card{background:var(--c1);border:1px solid var(--br);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .15s,transform .15s}
.source-card:hover{border-color:var(--br2);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.sc-top{padding:16px 18px 12px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px}
.sc-ico{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0}
.sc-ico.gr{background:var(--grx)}.sc-ico.vi{background:var(--vix)}.sc-ico.am{background:var(--amx)}.sc-ico.cy{background:var(--cyx)}.sc-ico.re{background:var(--rex)}.sc-ico.pk{background:var(--pkx)}
.sc-info{flex:1;min-width:0}
.sc-name{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t1);margin-bottom:2px}
.sc-source{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9.5px;color:var(--t3);margin-bottom:6px}
.sc-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--t2);line-height:1.6}
.sc-body{padding:0 18px 14px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
.sc-divider{height:1px;background:var(--br);margin:0 18px}
.tag-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:5px}
.tag{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:20px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap}
.t-gr{background:var(--grx);color:var(--gr);border:1px solid rgba(0,208,132,.2)}
.t-vi{background:var(--vix);color:var(--vi);border:1px solid rgba(108,99,255,.2)}
.t-am{background:var(--amx);color:var(--am);border:1px solid rgba(255,159,67,.2)}
.t-cy{background:var(--cyx);color:var(--cy);border:1px solid rgba(34,211,238,.2)}
.t-re{background:var(--rex);color:var(--re);border:1px solid rgba(255,91,91,.2)}
.t-pk{background:var(--pkx);color:var(--pk);border:1px solid rgba(247,37,133,.2)}
.t-dim{background:var(--c3);color:var(--t3);border:1px solid var(--br)}

.sc-feature{background:var(--c2);border-radius:8px;padding:9px 12px}
.sf-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:8.5px;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--t3);margin-bottom:6px}
.sf-items{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
.sf-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:11.5px;color:var(--t2)}
.sf-item::before{content:'→';color:var(--vi);font-size:10px;flex-shrink:0}

.sc-api{background:var(--bg);border-radius:6px;padding:8px 11px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10.5px;color:var(--t3);overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap}
.sc-api span{color:var(--gr)}

.impact-bar{padding:9px 12px;background:var(--c2);border-radius:8px}
.ib-label{font-size:9px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;color:var(--t3);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:6px}
.ib-items{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px}
.ib-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px}
.ib-name{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--t2);flex:1}
.ib-track{flex:1;height:4px;background:var(--c4);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden}
.ib-fill{height:100%;border-radius:2px}

/* ── PRIORITY MATRIX ── */
.matrix{background:var(--c1);border:1px solid var(--br);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:18px}
.matrix-hd{padding:14px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--br);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between}
.matrix-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t1)}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}
thead th{padding:9px 14px;text-align:left;font-size:8.5px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--t3);background:var(--c2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--br);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-weight:400}
thead th:first-child{padding-left:18px}
td{padding:10px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--br);font-size:12.5px;vertical-align:middle}
td:first-child{padding-left:18px}
tbody tr:last-child td{border:none}
tbody tr:hover td{background:rgba(255,255,255,.015)}
.td-main{font-weight:600;color:var(--t1)}
.td-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--t3);margin-top:2px}
.td-code{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--t2)}

/* ── CODE SNIPPET ── */
.code-card{background:var(--bg);border:1px solid var(--br);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:10px}
.code-hd{padding:9px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--br);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;background:var(--c1)}
.code-lang{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--t3);letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase}
.code-copy{font-size:10px;color:var(--vi);background:var(--vix);border:none;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit}
pre{padding:14px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11.5px;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.7}
.kw{color:#C792EA}.str{color:#C3E88D}.fn{color:#82AAFF}.cm{color:#546E7A;font-style:italic}.num{color:#F78C6C}.prop{color:#FFCB6B}

/* ── FEATURE BOX ── */
.feature-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(108,99,255,.08),rgba(34,211,238,.04));border:1px solid rgba(108,99,255,.2);border-radius:14px;padding:20px 22px;margin-bottom:18px}
.fb-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t1);margin-bottom:6px}
.fb-sub{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--t2);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:14px}
.fb-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px}
.fb-item{background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid var(--br);border-radius:8px;padding:11px 13px}
.fbi-n{font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gr);font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;line-height:1}
.fbi-l{font-size:11px;color:var(--t3);margin-top:3px}

/* ── NOTICE ── */
.notice{padding:12px 16px;border-radius:9px;font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:18px;display:flex;gap:10px}
.n-icon{font-size:14px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.notice.gr{background:var(--grx);border:1px solid rgba(0,208,132,.2);color:#8EFFD9}
.notice.am{background:var(--amx);border:1px solid rgba(255,159,67,.2);color:#FFCB8F}
.notice.vi{background:var(--vix);border:1px solid rgba(108,99,255,.2);color:#C4BFFF}

/* ── PHASE TIMELINE ── */
.timeline{display:flex;gap:0;margin-bottom:18px;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--br)}
.phase{flex:1;padding:16px;border-right:1px solid var(--br);background:var(--c1)}
.phase:last-child{border:none}
.phase-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:8.5px;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:6px;font-weight:500}
.phase-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--t1);margin-bottom:8px}
.phase-items{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--t3);line-height:1.8}

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media(max-width:900px){.grid-3,.grid-4{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.timeline{flex-direction:column}.phase{border-right:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--br)}.phase:last-child{border:none}}
@media(max-width:600px){.grid-2,.grid-3,.grid-4{grid-template-columns:1fr}.fb-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">InvestingPro.in — Data Intelligence Map</div>
  <h1>Free Data That Builds <span>Authority</span></h1>
  <div class="hero-sub">Every free, open-source, and public dataset available for Indian personal finance — mapped to platform features, traffic potential, and build sequence. No licensing fees. All legal. All authoritative.</div>
  <div class="hero-chips">
    <span class="hc gr">26 Data Sources</span>
    <span class="hc vi">8 Content Verticals</span>
    <span class="hc am">1.8M+ Potential Monthly Visits</span>
    <span class="hc cy">₹0 Data Cost</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- OPPORTUNITY OVERVIEW -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="feature-box">
    <div class="fb-title">The Data Opportunity in Numbers</div>
    <div class="fb-sub">InvestingPro can power every feature with 100% free, authoritative government and open-source data — the same data BankBazaar and GoodReturns use, but you build better tools around it.</div>
    <div class="fb-grid">
      <div class="fb-item"><div class="fbi-n">80,200+</div><div class="fbi-l">IFSC codes (Razorpay OS)</div></div>
      <div class="fb-item"><div class="fbi-n">16,000+</div><div class="fbi-l">Mutual fund schemes (AMFI)</div></div>
      <div class="fb-item"><div class="fbi-n">1.6M+</div><div class="fbi-l">PIN codes in India (data.gov.in)</div></div>
      <div class="fb-item"><div class="fbi-n">100+</div><div class="fbi-l">RBI macro indicators (DBIE API)</div></div>
      <div class="fb-item"><div class="fbi-n">200+</div><div class="fbi-l">Bank holiday entries/year (RBI)</div></div>
      <div class="fb-item"><div class="fbi-n">Daily</div><div class="fbi-l">Gold/silver MCX rates (IBJA)</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 1. PROGRAMMATIC SEO DATA -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-hd">
    <div class="section-label">Tier 1 — Highest Traffic Impact</div>
    <div class="section-title">Programmatic SEO Powerhouses</div>
    <div class="section-sub">These datasets generate thousands of pages automatically. Each page targets a specific search query. Total potential: 1.5M+ monthly visits from these alone.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="source-grid grid-2">

    <!-- IFSC -->
    <div class="source-card">
      <div class="sc-top">
        <div class="sc-ico gr">🏦</div>
        <div class="sc-info">
          <div class="sc-name">Razorpay IFSC Dataset</div>
          <div class="sc-source">ifsc.razorpay.com · GitHub MIT License · Free forever</div>
          <div class="sc-desc">Complete database of every bank branch in India with IFSC, MICR, NEFT/RTGS/IMPS/UPI support flags, address, contact, and geo data. Updated via automated scraper from RBI sources.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sc-divider"></div>
      <div class="sc-body">
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag t-gr">80,200+ branches</span>
          <span class="tag t-gr">MIT License</span>
          <span class="tag t-am">1.29M searches/mo</span>
          <span class="tag t-cy">REST API live</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-api"><span>GET</span> https://ifsc.razorpay.com/{IFSC_CODE}</div>
        <div class="sc-feature">
          <div class="sf-label">What to build with this</div>
          <div class="sf-items">
            <div class="sf-item">80,200 individual IFSC lookup pages (/ifsc/HDFC0000123)</div>
            <div class="sf-item">Bank directory pages by state/city/bank name</div>
            <div class="sf-item">Branch-level data enriched with nearby ATMs/services</div>
            <div class="sf-item">IFSC validator widget embed on every page</div>
            <div class="sf-item">Download complete JSON dataset for Next.js SSG</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-bar">
          <div class="ib-label">Traffic Potential</div>
          <div class="ib-items">
            <div class="ib-row"><span class="ib-name">IFSC lookup queries</span><div class="ib-track"><div class="ib-fill" style="width:95%;background:var(--gr)"></div></div><span style="font-size:10px;color:var(--gr);font-family:monospace">1.29M/mo</span></div>
            <div class="ib-row"><span class="ib-name">Bank branch searches</span><div class="ib-track"><div class="ib-fill" style="width:60%;background:var(--am)"></div></div><span style="font-size:10px;color:var(--am);font-family:monospace">240K/mo</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MF NAV -->
    <div class="source-card">
      <div class="sc-top">
        <div class="sc-ico vi">📈</div>
        <div class="sc-info">
          <div class="sc-name">AMFI Daily NAV — mfapi.in</div>
          <div class="sc-source">amfiindia.com · mfapi.in · Free public API</div>
          <div class="sc-desc">Every mutual fund scheme's NAV updated daily by AMFI. mfapi.in wraps it into a clean REST API with historical data. 16,000+ schemes. The authoritative source — same data Zerodha and Groww use.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sc-divider"></div>
      <div class="sc-body">
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag t-gr">16,000+ schemes</span>
          <span class="tag t-gr">Daily updates</span>
          <span class="tag t-vi">Historical NAV</span>
          <span class="tag t-cy">CORS enabled</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-api"><span>GET</span> https://api.mfapi.in/mf/{schemeCode}</div>
        <div class="sc-feature">
          <div class="sf-label">What to build with this</div>
          <div class="sf-items">
            <div class="sf-item">Live NAV table on every fund page — updated daily</div>
            <div class="sf-item">Fund performance charts (1Y/3Y/5Y returns auto-calculated)</div>
            <div class="sf-item">SIP return calculator with real historical NAV data</div>
            <div class="sf-item">CAGR comparison across fund categories</div>
            <div class="sf-item">Best performing funds widget on homepage</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-bar">
          <div class="ib-label">Traffic Potential</div>
          <div class="ib-items">
            <div class="ib-row"><span class="ib-name">MF NAV searches</span><div class="ib-track"><div class="ib-fill" style="width:75%;background:var(--vi)"></div></div><span style="font-size:10px;color:var(--vi);font-family:monospace">~450K/mo</span></div>
            <div class="ib-row"><span class="ib-name">Fund comparison queries</span><div class="ib-track"><div class="ib-fill" style="width:50%;background:var(--cy)"></div></div><span style="font-size:10px;color:var(--cy);font-family:monospace">~180K/mo</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Gold -->
    <div class="source-card">
      <div class="sc-top">
        <div class="sc-ico am">🥇</div>
        <div class="sc-info">
          <div class="sc-name">Gold & Silver Daily Rates — IBJA</div>
          <div class="sc-source">indiagoldratesapi.com · MCX · IBJA · Free tier available</div>
          <div class="sc-desc">India Bullion and Jewellers Association (IBJA) publishes authenticated daily gold and silver rates. Updated every morning. City-level rates vary slightly. "Aaj sone ka bhav" is one of India's most searched queries.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sc-divider"></div>
      <div class="sc-body">
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag t-am">Daily rates</span>
          <span class="tag t-am">City-level data</span>
          <span class="tag t-gr">IBJA authenticated</span>
          <span class="tag t-dim">22K/24K variants</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-api"><span>GET</span> https://indiagoldratesapi.com/api/rates</div>
        <div class="sc-feature">
          <div class="sf-label">What to build with this</div>
          <div class="sf-items">
            <div class="sf-item">Gold rate by city pages (100 cities = 100 programmatic pages)</div>
            <div class="sf-item">Historical gold price chart with 52-week high/low</div>
            <div class="sf-item">Gold rate calculator (grams to rupees widget)</div>
            <div class="sf-item">SGB vs physical gold vs gold ETF comparison tool</div>
            <div class="sf-item">Today's rate in homepage announcement bar</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="impact-bar">
          <div class="ib-label">Traffic Potential</div>
          <div class="ib-items">
            <div class="ib-row"><span class="ib-name">"Aaj sone ka bhav"</span><div class="ib-track"><div class="ib-fill" style="width:88%;background:var(--am)"></div></div><span style="font-size:10px;color:var(--am);font-family:monospace">~2.4M/mo</span></div>
            <div class="ib-row"><span class="ib-name">Gold rate [city]</span><div class="ib-track"><div class="ib-fill" style="width:65%;background:var(--am)"></div></div><span style="font-size:10px;color:var(--am);font-family:monospace">~600K/mo</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PIN Codes -->
    <div class="source-card">
      <div class="sc-top">
        <div class="sc-ico cy">📮</div>
        <div class="sc-info">
          <div class="sc-name">PIN Code Directory — data.gov.in</div>
          <div class="sc-source">data.gov.in · Ministry of Communications · Free API</div>
          <div class="sc-desc">All India PIN code directory from Department of Posts. Every PIN code with district, division, state, office name, and type. 19,100+ post offices. Free API key from data.gov.in — no cost.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sc-divider"></div>
      <div class="sc-body">
        <div class="tag-row">
          <span class="tag t-cy">154,000+ PIN codes</span>
          <span class="tag t-gr">Free API key</span>
          <span class="tag t-vi">All states covered</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-api"><span>GET</span> https://data.gov.in/api/datastore/resource/{id}?filters[pincode]={pin}</div>
        <div class="sc-feature">
          <div class="sf-label">What to build with this</div>
          <div class="sf-items">
            <div class="sf-item">PIN code → nearest branches/ATMs lookup pages</div>
            <div class="sf-item">Local bank availability by PIN code (50K+ pages)</div>
            <div class="sf-item">Address autocomplete with IFSC enrichment</div>
            <div class="sf-item">District-level financial data hub pages</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<!-- 2. RBI MACRO DATA -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-hd">
    <div class="section-label">Tier 1 — Authority & Trust Signals</div>
    <div class="section-title">RBI Official Data — DBIE Portal</div>
    <div class="section-sub">Reserve Bank of India's Database on Indian Economy. 100+ macro indicators, all free. Direct from the source — not scraped. This is what makes InvestingPro the authoritative reference, not just another comparison site.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="notice vi"><span class="n-icon">💡</span><div>data.rbi.org.in is RBI's official open data portal. All data is free, machine-readable, and carries the highest possible authority signal for SEO. Being cited alongside "Source: RBI" is the Indian personal finance equivalent of citing a Supreme Court ruling.</div></div>
  <div class="source-grid grid-3">

    <div class="source-card">
      <div class="sc-top">
        <div class="sc-ico gr">📊</div>
        <div class="sc-info">
